title: NHK Great Nature 2013 The Diamond Highlands of Brazil 720p x264

The Diamond Highlands of Brazil

Nature Documentary hosted by Hideki Nagao, published by NHK broadcasted as part of NHK Great Nature series in 2013 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/d/d9/The-Diamond-Highlands-of-Brazil-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
"The world's most stunning views", a splendid table mountain, giant waterfalls cascading down precipices. The secrets of the previously unexplored Diamond Highlands of Brazil are unveiled.
